column2: SELECT TOP # albums.album as album, count(albums.album) as num, SUM(albums.TrackPrice) as AlbumPrice,          albums.ArtistName as Artist         FROM (SELECT a.Title AS album, t.UnitPrice as TrackPrice, ar.Name as ArtistName         FROM chinook.Track AS t         INNER JOIN chinook.Album AS a         ON a.AlbumId = t.AlbumId         INNER JOIN chinook.Artist as ar         ON ar.ArtistId = a.ArtistId) albums         GROUP BY albums.album, Artist         ORDER BY AlbumPrice DESC
